Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.36,0:00:38.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又来了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.41,0:00:41.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.00,0:02:18.00,biaoti,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暖和的温泉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.92,0:02:26.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直都受到铃她们的照顾
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.30,0:02:28.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做为男人真没用
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.19,0:02:31.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人  那是剑道吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.22,0:02:34.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  是剑道  是爷爷教我的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.12,0:02:37.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爷爷说男人就应该保护女人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.27,0:02:46.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男人必须要保护女孩不可吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.25,0:02:52.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说了什么奇怪的话了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.26,0:02:55.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看  这个岛上没有男孩
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.98,0:02:57.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以感觉有点难理解
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.89,0:03:00.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对于不知道男人的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.62,0:03:01.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从不依靠男人的铃来说
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.60,0:03:03.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算知道字面意思
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.67,0:03:04.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也无法真正理解吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.93,0:03:19.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.85,0:03:21.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在铃遇到危机的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.82,0:03:24.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是我能展现出男孩气概的话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.29,0:03:26.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她应该就能理解我的话的意思了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.33,0:03:36.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说如此  也许铃比我还要有力气
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.24,0:03:39.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要稍微休息一下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.68,0:03:40.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事  没事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.71,0:03:41.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.89,0:04:00.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的  冷静点
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.08,0:04:07.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地震  我讨厌地震
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.30,0:04:11.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要  别再摇我了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.81,0:04:17.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洗澡  洗澡了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.04,0:04:24.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和行人一起洗就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.54,0:04:30.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,铃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.03,0:04:33.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,铃　怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.66,0:04:38.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人  浴室干了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.43,0:04:43.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完蛋了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.28,0:04:49.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全岛的浴室居然都停了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.85,0:04:52.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再说  岛上所有的浴室都是温泉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.02,0:04:54.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一事实才更加让人吃惊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.28,0:04:56.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.60,0:04:57.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帮大忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.65,0:04:58.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多亏拜托了小凛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.69,0:05:02.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里 不用谢啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.58,0:05:02.14,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疼  疼  疼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.85,0:05:04.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,钉子？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.06,0:05:07.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊呀  手又滑了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.30,0:05:08.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能会滑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.69,0:05:09.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是说过了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.05,0:05:11.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是对姐姐大人下手的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.01,0:05:13.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会轻易饶你的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.45,0:05:24.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.58,0:05:30.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.86,0:05:37.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好喝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.95,0:05:39.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那边的两位
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.01,0:05:40.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帮点忙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.27,0:05:45.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  等一下我当然会帮助行人大人洗澡的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.44,0:05:46.20,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.27,0:05:50.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从头到脚趾任何能洗的地方都不会放过
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.37,0:05:51.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.11,0:05:53.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐大人真狡猾
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.49,0:06:02.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绫音就去烧水吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.88,0:06:07.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烧水  烧水  烧水…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.88,0:06:09.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乐…乐意之极
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.09,0:06:18.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么我要…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.97,0:06:26.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水温正好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.09,0:06:28.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厉害  厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.27,0:06:35.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.08,0:06:37.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一  二
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.68,0:06:53.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绫音能再暖一点吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.70,0:06:58.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在做
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.57,0:07:01.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.81,0:07:07.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托  拜托  拜托  拜托…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.49,0:07:14.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,右边安全  左边安全
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.25,0:07:40.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼  真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.78,0:07:47.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈  真舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.78,0:07:51.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既打水  又劈柴烧火
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.28,0:07:54.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洗澡都那么辛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.53,0:07:56.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.65,0:07:59.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是无法想象一个按钮就能解决的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.98,0:08:00.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  喂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.41,0:08:02.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.34,0:08:03.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水温好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.16,0:08:07.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看的一清二楚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.67,0:08:09.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊咧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.48,0:08:12.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于这样了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.46,0:08:16.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清爽了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.06,0:08:19.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工作之后  本想洗个澡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.79,0:08:21.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到没有水了  真是吃了一惊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.98,0:08:24.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  全岛的温泉居然都停水了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.92,0:08:26.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟是什么原因
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.61,0:08:28.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然和地震有什么关系吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.15,0:08:31.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才的好剧烈啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.43,0:08:34.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天开始就要郁闷了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.48,0:08:38.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实在无法想象没有温泉的生活啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.69,0:08:40.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈哈哈
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.60,0:08:43.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实不用每天都要洗澡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.36,0:08:46.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用湿毛巾擦洗身体
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.29,0:08:48.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或在海中洗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.05,0:08:50.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,方法有很多…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.08,0:08:55.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说了什么不能说的话吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.35,0:08:57.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常不好的卫生状况
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.68,0:08:59.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不把汗水洗掉会很不舒服的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.99,0:09:02.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人大人不洁净
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.48,0:09:05.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要是不洗澡  饭都吃不好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.82,0:09:07.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且进到海里的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.38,0:09:09.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会因为盐变得粘乎乎的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.02,0:09:11.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.14,0:09:13.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用男人的标准来考虑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.65,0:09:15.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是不合适的发言
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.24,0:09:19.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的  明天开始洗澡该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.75,0:09:22.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然想一早就去修
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.36,0:09:26.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这周可是从早到晚都有大量的工作要做
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.31,0:09:49.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对女孩来说  洗澡真重要呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.56,0:09:56.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  让我来助你们一臂之力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.48,0:10:06.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好  行人？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.38,0:10:10.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去看看温泉的情况  行人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.70,0:10:24.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沿这个上去就能达到温泉的源头了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.66,0:10:35.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对有恐高症的我来说还真辛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.71,0:10:51.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然又这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.46,0:10:53.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难得才上去的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.97,0:11:13.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.18,0:11:17.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪乃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.31,0:11:24.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不单救了我  还送我上来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.25,0:11:25.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.19,0:11:26.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么  没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.33,0:11:27.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是吃一惊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.37,0:11:29.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和小鹰在早晨散步的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.45,0:11:31.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人忽然从天而降了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.01,0:11:33.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从天而降…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.61,0:11:34.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.51,0:11:35.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下面就交给我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.23,0:11:38.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傍晚的时候温泉就会恢复原样了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.58,0:11:39.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.18,0:11:42.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然  没有澡洗真痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.29,0:11:45.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小凛  工作那边没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.18,0:11:47.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用担心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.94,0:11:50.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说让我彻底修好才回去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.54,0:11:52.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.69,0:11:53.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.56,0:11:56.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.17,0:11:57.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,铃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.22,0:11:59.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.96,0:12:08.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来是沙土把温泉给堵住了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.91,0:12:11.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把大家带来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.28,0:12:13.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帮大忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.78,0:12:16.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我去了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.54,0:12:22.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好深啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.84,0:12:24.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉有点闷呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.07,0:12:27.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  因为这下面是温泉嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.92,0:12:29.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.92,0:12:37.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好烫 好烫 好烫…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.30,0:12:40.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.21,0:12:44.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.73,0:12:50.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  了解
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.26,0:13:00.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一  二  一  二…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.72,0:13:07.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.88,0:13:08.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.34,0:13:12.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好热啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.85,0:13:14.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何况又是在窄小的地方作业
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.63,0:13:18.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也脱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.35,0:13:23.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就凉爽了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.24,0:13:29.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这边反而身体又热了许多
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.38,0:13:35.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该已经挖了许多  还没出来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.53,0:13:37.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该马上就出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.34,0:13:40.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,温泉不会干枯了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.47,0:13:42.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.38,0:13:44.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀  只是假设而已
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.61,0:13:46.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洗澡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.21,0:13:49.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事  再挖一下就会出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.57,0:13:52.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炸猪排  怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.13,0:14:10.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地…地震？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.26,0:14:10.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.70,0:14:14.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公子  铃  快抓住
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.04,0:14:29.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,铃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.50,0:14:36.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,铃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.01,0:14:38.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.67,0:14:50.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人  炸猪排
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.26,0:14:52.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.08,0:14:54.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.47,0:14:56.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是比刚才那里更深的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.85,0:15:00.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那种井下居然有这样的洞窟
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.15,0:15:03.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之从下来的井口出去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.41,0:15:07.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个在我们掉下来之后
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.58,0:15:10.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像被封住了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.55,0:15:14.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么不是出不去了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.32,0:15:15.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.91,0:15:23.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看  有风在流动就是说明与外界相通
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.45,0:15:24.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.52,0:15:30.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.55,0:15:35.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.95,0:15:39.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能站起来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.89,0:15:41.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  没事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.17,0:15:44.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受伤了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.83,0:15:46.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.55,0:15:47.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.16,0:16:12.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的  没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.64,0:16:15.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别勉强  快  去找出口吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.94,0:16:35.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是出口
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.09,0:16:37.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.19,0:16:42.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  那么高的地方要怎么出去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.65,0:16:49.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快想想  行人  绝对要救出铃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.65,0:17:01.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以等等吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.64,0:17:03.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.49,0:17:09.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水有点温暖
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.34,0:17:16.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好烫
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.63,0:17:18.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.95,0:17:23.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这石头把温泉堵住了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.90,0:17:26.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人要怎么做
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.25,0:17:29.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能把温泉口稍微打开一点的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.77,0:17:31.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为里面的水压
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.11,0:17:32.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穴口应该会一口气被冲破
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.37,0:17:36.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涌出的温泉会把我们一口气冲起来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.39,0:17:37.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,温泉也能复活了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.81,0:17:38.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正所谓一石二鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.20,0:17:54.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.17,0:18:16.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.74,0:18:31.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.94,0:18:37.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.77,0:18:40.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  好烫
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.60,0:18:41.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.49,0:18:48.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.20,0:19:30.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,铃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.52,0:19:37.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,铃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.87,0:19:57.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么…可能放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.39,0:20:02.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.74,0:20:04.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,铃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.45,0:20:17.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等着啊  公子  铃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.90,0:20:26.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.75,0:20:33.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一件事解决了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.90,0:20:35.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,铃？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.82,0:20:38.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人  你这笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.36,0:20:41.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在救到我之前  就会死的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.26,0:20:42.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没这么夸张吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.91,0:20:46.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是行人也受了许多伤
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.35,0:20:48.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没事的
